{"tid":1094680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得 連登好應該要強制推廣台灣用語？","createTime":"2019-04-06T13:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T13:53:23.000Z","uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"40a7bdbe2039d023c982463d1f9d72384d1bd255","tid":1094680,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:03:54.000Z","msg":"台語咁好聽 好應該要強推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「蛋撻」要叫「蛋塔」<br />\n「薯仔」叫「洋芋」 「芝士」要叫「起司」<br />\n<br />\n以後唔準講「仆街喇」<br />\n應該講「靠北」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「講乜鳩」都唔比用<br />\n以後一律要叫「公三小」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學好台語 您我做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一份正評 一份支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966c84732aa76bf774fa8dedcedb5ed82b03b590","tid":1094680,"uid":17510,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:06:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔用返廣東話"},{"pid":"d7d8edf3f4b66565fb6c0b897f6dd9f547c915ea","tid":1094680,"uid":48577,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"樓主 呢到我頂到十秒<br />\n你快d走"},{"pid":"6839351ce79debb1dd2844ad6b87d976f41cd139","tid":1094680,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"966c84732aa76bf774fa8dedcedb5ed82b03b590","tid":1094680,"uid":17510,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:06:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔用返廣東話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"做乜要用廣東話 咁柒d字眼"},{"pid":"a9af7ac0bf1e5b5088b4e00380b09eb31561adc2","tid":1094680,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1010196ccb99025bec6f81e9e786399e234c8d64","tid":1094680,"uid":165782,"